{"tid":664292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Boring Company 首條洛杉磯隧道即將完工 數月後提供免費試坐","createTime":"2018-05-14T03:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T07:50:41.000Z","uid":53379,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"662afb1e1fb9b5aad807e640d4ce160c669db89a","tid":664292,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Boring Company 首條洛杉磯隧道即將完工 數月後提供免費試坐</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dims-6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fdims-6.jpeg&h=fab1c176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nElon Musk 旗下的隧道公司 Boring Company 在洛杉磯的試驗隧道即將完工，他表示當工程完成，而且取得相關部門的批准之後，就會向公衆提供免費試坐。<br />\n<br />\n在 Boring Company 的洛杉磯隧道網計劃中，第一期（下圖紅色部分）長 10.4 公里，將會首先作為概念實踐用途，用來示範技術和進行安全測試等。而藍色的部分則仍然在計劃當中，需要繼續徵求當地機構和公衆的意見，才會繼續發展這個隧道網。Elon Musk 最近分享的隧道影片，應該只是第一期隧道的一部分，但他表示這部分將會很快完成，並且開放公衆試坐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/boring-company-la-map-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fboring-company-la-map-4.jpg&h=f3ebf9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前 Boring Company 的技術方面已經沒有大問題，只是在獲得市民支持和機構批准方面仍然需要更多時間。開放公衆試坐將有望解釋當地居民的疑慮，從而提升隧道計劃的接受程度。Elon Musk 表示，隧道將會讓大衆運輸和單車優先使用，減低交通的成本。如果真的能夠成事，說不定可以有效減輕洛杉磯塞車嚴重的問題。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/13/elon-musk-la-boring-tunnel-video/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2Felon-musk-la-boring-tunnel-video%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=EwhOuvz2HvLuaSm4vdS%2F5Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7269d096\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/13/elon-musk-la-boring-tunnel-video/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"1e9b4ae4c1125ef6c1735a7bd3b3cebf70715b54","tid":664292,"uid":119979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"反觀高鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2145b51cace24522dac6f93ee9942aa958f65026","tid":664292,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"好想知哩啲隧道係點樣頂住地震<br />\n日本又係"},{"pid":"99fef7c888bdcaa1f6adb825e83f9860ba6dc81c","tid":664292,"uid":156005,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"2145b51cace24522dac6f93ee9942aa958f65026","tid":664292,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"好想知哩啲隧道係點樣頂住地震<br />\n日本又係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"地震來臨時隧道還安全嗎？<br />\n<br />\n設計合理的隧道，是地震來臨時最安全的地方。從結構安全的角度來看，與地面相比，隧道均勻的建設在地面以下。另外，即使破壞性巨大的地震會造成大量廢墟，也不會對隧道內部造成影響。以下案例供參考：<br />\n<br />\n    1994 年 Northridge 地震：地鐵隧道毫髮無損<br />\n    1989 年 Loma Prieta（北加州）地震：隧道沒有損壞，並用於運送救援人員<br />\n    1985 年墨西哥城地震：隧道沒有損壞，並用於運送救援人員<br />\n<br />\n最緊要造工好，大陸就唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cabbe703248553a721e5b3fbd01304fd195d0c","tid":664292,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會有風馳電制既感覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc4654d902bb3590cb17eec80a79adebc1ac5a5","tid":664292,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99fef7c888bdcaa1f6adb825e83f9860ba6dc81c","tid":664292,"uid":156005,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"2145b51cace24522dac6f93ee9942aa958f65026","tid":664292,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"好想知哩啲隧道係點樣頂住地震<br />\n日本又係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"地震來臨時隧道還安全嗎？<br />\n<br />\n設計合理的隧道，是地震來臨時最安全的地方。從結構安全的角度來看，與地面相比，隧道均勻的建設在地面以下。另外，即使破壞性巨大的地震會造成大量廢墟，也不會對隧道內部造成影響。以下案例供參考：<br />\n<br />\n    1994 年 Northridge 地震：地鐵隧道毫髮無損<br />\n    1989 年 Loma Prieta（北加州）地震：隧道沒有損壞，並用於運送救援人員<br />\n    1985 年墨西哥城地震：隧道沒有損壞，並用於運送救援人員<br />\n<br />\n最緊要造工好，大陸就唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"又幾有道理<br />\n如果地底唔係安全 <br />\n點解美帝子民有事都會入地下室<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935085ae23e006a4ce45c8d7f22eb52dc46d2a58","tid":664292,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"hk 千億 二手科技"},{"pid":"fa9d46ff92b3f864abb7a8606b5f96edbd216d45","tid":664292,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"935085ae23e006a4ce45c8d7f22eb52dc46d2a58","tid":664292,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"hk 千億 二手科技"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"俾人貪哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f4852872220e52d00d6c04f20332918ed29803","tid":664292,"uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"可以行單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50fce12247131b5e12c74e4f441bafbfc38209c","tid":664292,"uid":550,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"美國人人有車先整出嚟啫<br />\n地底有位起地鐵咪仲符合經濟效益"},{"pid":"6d797e44343741a9543ce054eaac8cb44af8e590","tid":664292,"uid":91317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"入面做野係咪好悶？"},{"pid":"2824902d94cb8085ced9e91f09a412b01f0165ba","tid":664292,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:58:39.000Z","msg":"反觀我們千幾億 ..."},{"pid":"37aca8aaab48b5388a4734948842da923704e9a4","tid":664292,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"Elon Mask真係好癲"},{"pid":"a117572dedef062f7fb369867ca4480b480929e7","tid":664292,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14